      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Karlsruhe ¶ 30 November 1879 ¶ Grandducal Garden Administration ¶ Your honour ¶  ¶ Dr W. Sonder ¶  from Hamburg informed me that he has sent a parcel to you destined for me with other natural history ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M79.11.30</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Carl Mayer to [Ferdinand von Krauss]</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Staatliches Museum für Naturkunde, Stuttgart.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in; text-align: end; text-indent: 0.4929in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>Carlsruhe,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in; text-align: end; text-indent: 0.4929in; "
               xml:lang="de">d. 30ten Nov. 1879</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Grossherzogl. GARTEN-DIRECTION.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Euer Hochgeboren!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Herr Dr. W. Sonder aus Hamburg theilt mir mit, dass er ein für mich bestimmtes Packet mit anderen naturhistorischen Gegenständen an Sie abgesandt habe, mit dem Ersuchen, selbes gefälligst an mich befördern zu wollen. </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sollten Sie während dessen in den Besitz hievon gekommen seyn, so bitte ich um bald gefällige Übermittlung.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit hochachtungsvoller Ergebenheit zeichnet</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>C. Mayer</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Karlsruhe</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">30 November 1879</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Grandducal Garden Administration</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Your honour</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dr W. Sonder<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See W. Sonder to F. von Krauss, 20 November 1879, for reference to this material. 143 orchids and 104 ferns sent by Mueller.</p>
               </note> from Hamburg informed me that he has sent a parcel to you destined for me with other natural history objects, with the request to be willing to kindly forward it on to me. </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Should you have come into the possession of it in the meantime, I ask you for kindly transmission soon.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With respectful devotion signs</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>C. Mayer</p>
         </div>
